definition.text: These are the Pools, Assets, Features, and Positions hierarchies used to produce granular definitions of the Superalgos Project to be used for governance.

translations.text: Это иерархии Pools, Assets, Features и Positions, используемые для создания детальных определений проекта Superalgos, которые будут использоваться для управления.

paragraphs.text: Right click and Edit to enter edit mode and change this text. ENTER to write new paragraphs. ESC to exit edit mode. Then you can use docs.save to save your changes and app.contribute to send it to the main repository.
